&lt;p&gt;Ready to dive into the world of smart tech and help build the future of IoT? As a Technical Support Engineering Intern, you won&#39;t be grabbing coffee or shadowing others. Our interns are at the forefront of our team, tackling real-world challenges alongside our full-time engineers. Based at our San Mateo HQ, you&#39;ll work with cutting-edge, cloud-managed IoT technology, helping our enterprise clients with everything from troubleshooting to system design.&lt;/p&gt;
