&lt;p&gt;To achieve our mission, we’re seeking a very specific candidate. We want someone who is passionate about our mission and who believes in the power of crypto and blockchain technology to update the financial system. We want someone who is eager to leave their mark on the world, who relishes the pressure and privilege of working with high caliber colleagues, and who actively seeks feedback to keep leveling up. We want someone who will run towards, not away from, solving the company’s hardest problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/mission&quot;&gt;work culture&lt;/a&gt; is intense and isn’t for everyone. But if you want to build the future alongside others who excel in their disciplines and expect the same from you, there’s no better place to be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While many roles at Coinbase are remote-first, we are not remote-only. In-person participation is required throughout the year. Team and company-wide offsites are held multiple times annually to foster collaboration, connection, and alignment. Attendance is expected and fully supported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a 12-week internship during summer 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Internal Audit Function at Coinbase works to enhance and protect organizational value by providing independent, risk-based, objective assurance and advisory services designed to add value and improve the Company&#39;s operations. The Internal Audit Function helps Coinbase accomplish its objectives by bringing a systematic, disciplined approach to evaluate and improve the effectiveness of governance, compliance, risk management, and control processes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Coinbase Internal Audit function is looking for interns to join the team. Individuals will be able to get hands-on experience supporting Compliance and Operational audits, while also helping shape the future of the department by supporting its Professional Practices Group. These roles are based in the UK or Luxembourg (Remote) and will be reporting to an Internal Audit Manager. Each individual will be responsible for learning and supporting all aspects of audits, including planning, testing and report writing. In addition, individuals will support the team with critical audit activities, such as validations of audit and regulatory findings, risk assessments and other audit relevant activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the team in exploring how new ideas and technology, like AI, can improve our audits and audit processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support a variety of Compliance and Operational audits by conducting testing, documentation, and preparing findings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create accurate, logical and detailed work-papers clearly describing the work performed, testing results and conclusions for audit projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, maintain, and validate IA process documentation with control/process owners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present findings and recommendations to IA leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your problem-solving skills and attention to detail to contribute to team projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for crypto&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mission focused&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work with a team and engage stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quick, inquisitive learner. Always ready to adapt and learn something new&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in emerging technologies, like AI, and a curiosity on how they can be used in audit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for process improvement and finding smarter ways of working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter who can run with projects to completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem solving skills and strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication (written and verbal), and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized, enthusiastic, and motivated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing a BA/BS degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coursework or personal project related to AI or process automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate to advanced experience with data analytics or visualization tools (e.g. Tableau, SQL, Power BI, Python)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of internal controls or risk management concepts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Google Suite and Microsoft Excel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated passion for and knowledge of the Crypto industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
