&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxvz75zloz83zo2z72zz80zz80zz70zbrz68z7xbf25wobz87zivsz71z7z87zz89z&quot;&gt;As a Technical Content Developer in the Knowledge, Experience, &amp;amp; Platforms&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxvz75zloz83zo2z72zz80zz80zz70zbrz68z7xbf25wobz87zivsz71z7z87zz89z h-lparen&quot;&gt;(KXP)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxvz75zloz83zo2z72zz80zz80zz70zbrz68z7xbf25wobz87zivsz71z7z87zz89z&quot;&gt; org you will play a crucial role in ensuring our self-serve teams can confidently adopt, implement, and grow with Dropbox products. You will work with the Technical Content Strategist to execute and deliver clear, scalable, and impactful technical documentation that enables customer success across a range of use cases—from integrations and setup, to long-term support and expansion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxvz75zloz83zo2z72zz80zz80zz70zbrz68z7xbf25wobz87zivsz71z7z87zz89z&quot;&gt;This is a highly collaborative role that sits at the intersection of product, support enablement, and customer enablement. You’ll work closely with cross-functional teams to develop content that not only tells the technical story of Dropbox, but empowers users of all levels to get the most out of the Dropbox product suite.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovvz89zm3h9z75zl1z87z2qdz81zz85zfisz71zp08z77zz77zez70zuu9z70zz81z&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
