&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zctypz68zz88znaz83zrdwz73zcvz80z8z72z75z72zsh25z80zgz86zz72z&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a Video Content Design Intern to support the creation and maintenance of customer-facing educational videos. In this role, you’ll work closely with content designers, multimedia partners, and cross-functional stakeholders to help update, organize, and publish video tutorials and learning content across Dropbox’s education platforms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
