&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zctypz68zz88znaz83zrdwz73zcvz80z8z72z75z72zsh25z80zgz86zz72z&quot;&gt;Strong attention to detail, clear communication skills, and ability to learn and follow established guidelines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
