&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zctypz68zz88znaz83zrdwz73zcvz80z8z72z75z72zsh25z80zgz86zz72z&quot;&gt;Experience editing video using tools such as Adobe Premiere Pro, including basic cuts, audio cleanup, and exporting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zctypz68zz88znaz83zrdwz73zcvz80z8z72z75z72zsh25z80zgz86zz72z&quot;&gt;Experience creating screen recordings or instructional videos using tools like Loom or similar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zctypz68zz88znaz83zrdwz73zcvz80z8z72z75z72zsh25z80zgz86zz72z&quot;&gt;Familiarity with preparing content for review and publication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
