&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvohjohz75zfgxr1tcz87zz67z4oz82zz75z7z67zz87zjz81zz90za5dz85zf&quot; data-highlight-color=&quot;#F7CC62&quot;&gt;Strong coding skills&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;highlight author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvohjohz75zfgxr1tcz87zz67z4oz82zz75z7z67zz87zjz81zz90za5dz85zf h-lparen&quot; data-highlight-color=&quot;#F7CC62&quot;&gt;(e.g.,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvohjohz75zfgxr1tcz87zz67z4oz82zz75z7z67zz87zjz81zz90za5dz85zf&quot; data-highlight-color=&quot;#F7CC62&quot;&gt; Python&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz80ziz80zz83zz89zz65z5z82zz87zpwqxz77zi19bcx4z76zz66zd0901z79zz89zg&quot; data-highlight-color=&quot;#F7CC62&quot;&gt;, PyTorch, scikit-learn, or similar ML libraries&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvohjohz75zfgxr1tcz87zz67z4oz82zz75z7z67zz87zjz81zz90za5dz85zf&quot; data-highlight-color=&quot;#F7CC62&quot;&gt;), plus an ability to quickly prototype and iterate on cutting-edge ideas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
