&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;PhD candidate in Computer Science or a related field graduating between Winter 2026 and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zplz75zz87z6z122z3mdlz67zz82zz73zjsz88zcbz82zhz72zz81zz83zez66zz77zz77zncd&quot;&gt;Spring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt; 202&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zplz75zz87z6z122z3mdlz67zz82zz73zjsz88zcbz82zhz72zz81zz83zez66zz77zz77zncd&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;Proven experience in systems/infrastructure &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotvez67zz84zgvz75ztjz67zz70z61jz73zaz73zz70ztz74zz65z59z79zz71zz67zocn6k&quot;&gt;and/or AI/ML &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;through research publications, significant projects, or internships where you built or tested advanced solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;Strong coding skills&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z h-lparen&quot;&gt;(e.g.,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt; Python, Rust, Go, C++) plus an ability to quickly prototype and iterate on cutting-edge ideas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;Curiosity and drive to explore novel systems methodologies and translate them into practical applications that solve practical needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95be4z82zez76z4mvz77zz78zz81zz79zv3z70zz72zz68zuz89zz66zrz88zz76zv2z83zz77zz122z&quot;&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration skills, especially in interdisciplinary teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
