&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zr28wz84z9z72zxpgz84zz85zz89zrz80zt722atz90zcjjsgkz69z&quot;&gt;You’ll either own a scoped qualitative research project or support ongoing research initiatives, depending on business needs, with guidance from experienced researchers. Your work may focus on a specific user workflow and will contribute to clear insights and actionable recommendations for product partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
