&lt;li&gt;Coursework or original content is totally fine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to commit to a minimum 12 week summer internship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In office 3-5 days a week in Lisbon.&lt;/li&gt;
